show.description: A billionaire CEO, Rajveer Khanna, hides his identity to win the heart of Ananya, a kind-hearted woman facing family betrayal. Their emotional journey intertwines love, secrets, and a quest to reunite Ananya with her long-lost daughter, culminating in a heartfelt family reunion.
